            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "……今朝、\r\nフクキタルの占いで言われたんです。",
            "enText": "…This morning, I had my fortune \ntold by Fukukitaru.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
